summary: Artist Choice vs Fans Punishment.
body:
Artist Choice vs Fans Punishment.

This is something I’ve noticed happening a LOT lately and I feel like someone has to address it-

There is nothing wrong with writing your OC with a horrific backstory, killing them, or even self-projecting your own bitter thoughts into them as a means. Nothing wrong at all.

However, there is a HUGE problem when you do it to specifically punish fans for haters actions.

No, this is different from drawing or writing something angsty to get a rise from readers with the intent of making them feel that way temporarily or even doing it at someone else’s request. That’s what your fans want to see.

Announcing that someone made you feel bad or that you’re annoyed AND THEN ANNOUNCING THAT YOU’RE GOING TO KILL OR HARM YOUR OC ANYWAY SO ITS FINE is a problem. It’s to get a rise out of people who hurt you AND the people who did nothing wrong.

Your fans can’t control someone else’s negative emotions. It’s not fair to punish something they’ve come to love due to someone else’s actions. Its manipulating the people who care about your work into hating someone for “making” a creator take away something they love.

Like I said before, there is NOTHING wrong with harming or killing your character for the sake of the story, but there IS a big problem when you’re using it as a threat.

There’s a BIG difference between “This is my artistic/personal choice and I feel it’s the right one to make.” And “THIS PERSON HATES MY WORK BUT ITS OKAY BECAUSE I’M KILLING MY OC ANYWAY. YOU HAPPY? THANKS A LOT!”

body:
New commission prices!

Hello everyone, since summer vacation has started I’ve been rolling out commissions. I don’t get any other income then this so it is officially my job now! There are some changes in my commission prices! I can take payment plans.

Please allow up to a month for your completed commission, I can work with deadlines for 5$

I take PayPal and google pay

Refunds and sketches are available at all times during the commission process

I do not do real pets or people, I can also do humans

DIGITAL BADGES!: I don’t have any examples right now but they would be 40$ and they would be a half body with a characters name below

Slots available: 5/5

HEADSHOTS: 35$+ according to complexity

Slots available: 5/5

CHIBIS: 40$+ according to complexity

Slots available: 5/5

FULL BODY FULL RENDER: 80$, I can accept payment plans for this option

Slots available: 3/3

CUSTOM CHARACTER: 60$, send me a moodboard and I can create a custom character just for you! Can be fursuit friendly if you ask
